{"tid":2084212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係盧曉欣同學死忌","createTime":"2020-06-29T06:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T07:30:44.000Z","uid":44025,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"695bfd726b3206ee1673228463dd69ee71b60017","tid":2084212,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"希望大家今日可以嚟粉嶺悼念盧同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbTpyqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbTpyqf.jpg&h=253a6584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yASHji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yASHji.jpg&h=9f18d032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【6.29 盧曉欣同學逝世一周年 】<br />\n日期：29/6(一）<br />\n時間：19:30 至 21:30<br />\n地點：嘉福邨福泰樓（對開的露天劇場）<br />\n<br />\n教育大學21歲女生盧曉欣，2019年6月29日在粉嶺嘉福邨留下「反送中」遺書後墮樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n致香港人：<br />\n雖然抗爭時間久了，<br />\n但絕對不能忘記，<br />\n我們一直以來的理念，<br />\n一定要堅持下去。<br />\n強烈要求全面撒回條例<br />\n收回暴動論 釋放學生示威者<br />\n林鄭下台 嚴懲警方<br />\n本人但願可以小命<br />\n成功換取二百萬人的心願<br />\n<br />\n請你們堅持下去！<br />\nLEST WE FORGET<br />\n<br />\n你忘掉她的說話了嗎<br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n-我們已取得管理處發出的活動許可批文<br />\n觀迎攜帶鮮花到場<br />\n<br />\n- 流水式悼念<br />\n- 宗教活動在私人地方舉行，受法例保障<br />\n- 請視實際安全情況參加活動<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：呂智恆Facebook"},{"pid":"3384c8eb93811943ca624654a9ba03ac6738d1e0","tid":2084212,"uid":4835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b5d24b959f1b6bc1416a28b6b32e24421009430","tid":2084212,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">你哋班連登仔， 喺連登圍爐洗版有撚用？</span><br />\n<br />\n我要見到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IG Facebook</span>  各大社交平台<br />\n都要見到呢幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7月1 維園見</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f71b810e7efd525247a8437c47bb30606eaee7a3","tid":2084212,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2111fb5cbd61aea1ccd7feddf2aa122c58dc11f3","tid":2084212,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365f8b9b7f311b3beb36c63ae7a4fa8e513fede7","tid":2084212,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"189087f0dd6e234368322f92fcee9bce4c078f96","tid":2084212,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"031609a00b2bf04e80abc5498ae8fb0573f58abf","tid":2084212,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9492563ac4a5025fb4aacb409345cd8358f6819e","tid":2084212,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"我哋要勇敢面對挑戰<br />\n面對困難要三思而行"},{"pid":"fa230106d82ea38ea7fb3d29eb074f56ed1a4621","tid":2084212,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}